title: STARFIELD is HERE! - Ray Gun Live
description:
Whoa, what a big day! I'm what you would call an epic gamist and I've been cautiously optimistic for this lil game for a while. Lets jump in and see what all the hullabaloooh is all about. I hope I can get married in this game so I can live out my fantasy of going through a messy divorce and running away to the deep reaches of space to flee the cold grasp of my bitch ex wife (possibly named Bethany or something) I hope this game can do that for me hahhahahahahahahaha
